data.description: Beautiful home sitting on over a quarter acre in a gated community! 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, 2 car garage and over 2,700 sq. ft.  Downstairs features wide open spaces with Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout, high ceilings, formal living room, formal dining room, breakfast nook, family room, laundry room, half bath and of course the absolutely gorgeous kitchen.  Kitchen offers a ton of counter space with granite counter tops, island, updated cabinets, stainless steal appliances, and a walk-in pantry! All bedrooms are upstairs along with a large game room with a closet and a full bathroom.  Secondary bedrooms all have nice walk-in closets.  Primary bedroom is expansive with high ceilings and a beautiful en-suite bathroom.  Master bathroom features double vanity, jetted jacuzzi tub, separate shower, linen closet and a ginormous master closet! Exterior offers one of the largest backyards in the neighborhood! A wonderful covered patio to enjoy the space out of the sun, and then a large concrete patio.  It is a blank canvas awaiting it's new owner's! Solar panels offer really low energy bills! Average Energy bill is around $60!! Location is convenient to Wal-Mart, shopping, restaurants, Fort Sam Houston and BAMC.  Easy commute to I-10, I-35, Loop 410 and Loop 1604!
